    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$18,500 - Honest, driver-quality classic in fair overall condition with plenty of charm and a price that makes it approachable. This is the kind of car you can enjoy right away while improving over time, with a respectable appearance and lots of appeal for someone who wants an affordable vintage cruiser rather than a show car. A solid entry point into classic car ownership for the buyer who appreciates character and value.",
