    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered honestly in poor overall condition and should be viewed as a budget car, project, or parts/repair candidate. It shows significant wear for its age and use, with noticeable cosmetic flaws, a tired interior, and signs that it will need work and ongoing attention. It is not a mint or turnkey example, and buyers should expect deferred maintenance, visible wear, and the possibility of mechanical issues. Best suited for someone who understands what they\u2019re looking at and wants an inexpensive vehicle with full awareness of its condition.",
