    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows clear wear consistent with age and use, but it presents a strong opportunity for a handy buyer, commuter, or anyone seeking low-cost wheels without overpaying. Straightforward, affordable, and priced to move.",
      "price": 4495.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option for someone handy, a project seeker, or anyone needing a low-cost set of wheels. Great candidate to tinker with, use around town, or make the most of as a practical starter. If you appreciate a car with character and opportunity, this could be a smart buy at a friendly price.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Strong project or budget daily with solid enthusiast appeal. Engine starts up, pulls through the rev range, and the drivetrain does what it should. Suspension, brakes, and steering are serviceable, making it a usable platform right now while leaving room for cosmetic and mechanical sorting over time. Not a showroom car, but a straightforward driver with good bones for someone who knows their way around maintenance and wants affordable entry into ownership. Priced to reflect condition and upside.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap runner. Rough around the edges, but priced to move. Great budget buy or project car. First with cash gets it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Turn heads without trying. This car has the kind of road-worn charm that modern vehicles spend years trying to imitate\u2014confident stance, timeless lines, and a presence that still feels right pulling up anywhere. It\u2019s an ideal choice for someone who sees more than transportation: a practical daily with personality, a weekend project with soul, or an affordable way into something that still feels special every time you walk up to it. If you appreciate character, potential, and a price that leaves room for your own vision, this one is easy to get excited about.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
