      "description": "Value-priced and ready to work, this vehicle is a practical choice for anyone seeking dependable basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age, but it starts, runs, and offers straightforward utility for commuting, errands, or as an inexpensive backup vehicle. A sensible buy for shoppers who appreciate honest condition and strong value.",
